title: Diploma in Administrative Procedures and Support in the Office
headline: Learn Administrative Procedures and Support in the Office with this free online course.
description: This free online course Administrative Procedures and Support in the Office teaches students about administrative procedures and skills for the office. The course will cover organization, time management, and verbal and non-verbal communication. The course wraps up with calendar management and goal setting. So, why wait? Start this course today and learn about Administrative Procedures and Support in the Office.
courseDescription:
This course, Administrative Procedures and Support in the Office, will provide you with an understanding of administrative office procedures. You will learn why your office needs administrative procedures. You will be able to explain how to gather the right tools and identify the procedures to include. You will also learn about the top five procedures to record and what not to include in the procedure guide.

This course then explains Administrative Support. You will learn about getting organized and managing your time. You will also learn about special tasks. Students will also learn about verbal and non-verbal communication skills. The module also teaches students about empowering themselves. The module then goes into the team of two and taking care of yourself.

This course then wraps up with a lesson on executive assistants. You will learn when to take the initiative as well as active listening and calendar management. Students will learn about communication skills, word processing, and goal setting. By taking this course you will learn about the importance of administrative procedures and support in the office. So why wait? Start learning today. 

Start Course Now

Once you have completed this course, you have the option to acquire an official Diploma, which is a great way to share your achievement with the world.

Your Alison is:
  • Ideal for sharing with potential employers
  • Include it in your CV, professional social media profiles and job applications.
  • An indication of your commitment to continuously learn, upskill & achieve high results.
  • An incentive for you to continue empowering yourself through lifelong learning.
Alison offers 3 types of Diplomas for completed Diploma courses:
  • Digital : a downloadable in PDF format immediately available to you when you complete your purchase.
  • : a physical version of your officially branded and security-marked , posted to you with FREE shipping.
  • Framed : a physical version of your officially branded and security marked in a stylish frame, posted to you with FREE shipping.

All are available to purchase through the Alison Shop. For more information on purchasing Alison , please visit our FAQs. If you decide not to purchase your Alison , you can still demonstrate your achievement by sharing your Learner Record or Learner Achievement Verification, both of which are accessible from your Dashboard.
